data.title: Charef, Djelfa, Algeria
data.text:
Charef, also known as Charet, is a municipality in Djelfa Province, Algeria, located at 34.6209800 latitude and 2.7950300 longitude. The area experiences a hot desert climate with little rainfall throughout the year. Its history and heritage remain relatively unexplored.
